Additional Governance and Attribution Terms:

1. CONTRIBUTOR ATTRIBUTION
All contributors to this project are recognized in lineage/contributor-registry.md
and maintain permanent documentation in the immutable record.

2. GOVERNANCE FRAMEWORK
Contributions are subject to the governance terms outlined in:
- governance/charter.md
- governance/amendment-protocol.md
- governance/licensing-ip.md
- governance/permissions-matrix.md

3. VERIFICATION AND INTEGRITY
All code and documentation in this project may be verified using:
- Cryptographic hashing (scripts/hashing.py)
- Digital signature verification (scripts/signature-verification.py)
- Blockchain anchors (anchors/blockchain-anchor.md)
- Timestamp proofs (anchors/timestamp-proof.md)

4. DISPUTES AND APPEALS
Licensing disputes are subject to procedures in:
- governance/oversight-appeals-sanctions.md

5. IP AND LICENSING
Individual contributor IP rights are documented in:
- governance/licensing-ip.md
- lineage/contributor-registry.md

See VERIFY.md for complete verification procedures and governance/charter.md
for the complete governance framework governing this software.
